Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{=6}---- Dialogue
Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.69,0:00:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...{*}no{*chan}. Hey, come on, listen!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.15,0:00:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.99,0:00:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.57,0:00:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah! Look at what I found!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.28,0:00:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oasis Festival?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.20,0:00:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This was back when the oasis\nwas still the size of a lake.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.58,0:00:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, for you. As a memento.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.46,0:00:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just precious?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.71,0:00:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What if a miracle happened\nand Abydos started thriving agai—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.55,0:00:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracles aren't real, {*}Yume{*Senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.30,0:00:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.30,0:00:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They only happen in fairy tales.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Face reality.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.68,0:00:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would {\i1}anyone{\i0}\never come to this wasteland?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.90,0:00:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even entertaining the idea is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.53,0:00:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.15,0:00:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.61,0:00:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All you do is go on and on\nabout useless stuff like miracles.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.07,0:00:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the president of the Abydos student council.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.33,0:01:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a lot of responsibilities,\nso start taking this more seriously!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Shiroko{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.48,0:02:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shiroko{**-chan}, got a second to talk?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.07,0:02:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,About yesterday, well... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.95,0:02:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I was also being too pushy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.70,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're just worried about li'l ol' me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.79,0:03:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Foreclosure Task Force isn't complete without you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, you're so sweet.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hoshino{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.76,0:03:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're hiding from us,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.47,0:03:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but I trust you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.81,0:03:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I really did luck out,\ngoing to the same school as you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.90,0:03:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how the land Abydos owned\nwas transferred to a third party?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.74,0:03:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We looked deeper into it,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.45,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and it turns out that the land is currently\nowned by a "Kaiser Construction".
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.71,0:03:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that means...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.75,0:03:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the Kaiser Corporation after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The only property we own\nis this building and its surroundings.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.38,0:04:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything else—the main building buried underneath\nthe sand, the miles of wasteland surrounding it, {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.01,0:04:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,even the infrastructure and land in the city—\nis owned by them now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All of that?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.65,0:04:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You usually can't trade land owned by a school district.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been the student council.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.78,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.44,0:04:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.07,0:04:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This deal originated from the student council.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? What were they thinking?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.87,0:04:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How could they have just handed over\nAbydos's land to those creeps?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.12,0:04:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows a school's district\nis the property of that school.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.05,0:04:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We were so focused on our debt that we never even\nimagined the council could have sold it off.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.26,0:04:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. If only I had realized this sooner...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it, Ayane{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.06,0:04:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This all happened long before any of us enro—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.90,0:04:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you on the student council, Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.53,0:04:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.49,0:05:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,\nyou were the vice president, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, y'know.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.87,0:05:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, it was just me and the president.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Just you two?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.62,0:05:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. By then, the student population\nhad already dropped into the double digits.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.63,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff had all up and left,\nand actual classes were a thing of the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.72,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the student council office\nwas just a glorified storage room.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.60,0:05:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The president was the biggest klutz at school,\nwith hardly a thought in her head.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.27,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, I was the new kid with {*}an{*the bad} attitude.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.48,0:05:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire situation was one big mess.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.86,0:05:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck? How is that even a student council?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.07,0:05:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We were nothing more than a couple of dum-dums\ndoing dumb things together at the end of the day.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.37,0:05:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, those were the days.\nAll we did was loiter around.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.87,0:05:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2690,4483,\c&HFDFDFD&\3c&HFDFDFD&\4c&HFDFDFD&)}Just two clueless idiots,\nstuck in their own little world.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.92,0:05:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't blame yourself for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.80,0:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened in the past,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.09,0:06:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but what I {\i1}do{\i0} know is that without you,\nthe Task Force wouldn't be what it is today.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always lazing about.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You never give a straight answer.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.73,0:06:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's barely the tip of the iceberg.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're always the first to step up when we need you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I respect you. {Clearly this should be translated as "I'm confessing to you" smh homophobic fansubbers --ML}{confess your crimes, shiroko --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where's this coming from, Shiroko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.28,0:06:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just drop a line like that out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.87,0:06:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,why did the student council sell their land\nto the Kaiser Corporation in the first place?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.29,0:06:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably did it to pay off their debt at first.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.17,0:06:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just my guess.\nI wasn't there when it happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.38,0:06:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they were trying their best for the school,\nbut the debts just kept piling up.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe so, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.31,0:06:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's unlikely all the land claimed\nby the desert had much value.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.48,0:06:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They may have paid back the interest,\nbut they couldn't have reduced the principal.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.02,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Which would have forced them\nto keep selling more and more land.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.61,0:07:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.36,0:07:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That means the deal was rigged from the start! {is that a NV reference --ML}{The bear and the bull --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.12,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be right about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.20,0:07:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.16,0:07:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,First, they give out a loan that could never be paid off.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.25,0:07:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, they pressure the school to sell their land\nin order to pay back what little of the debt they could.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That has to be it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.63,0:07:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the end of it, the entire school district\nwill have fallen into the Kaiser Corporation's hands.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.47,0:07:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.26,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This was probably their plan from the start.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.47,0:07:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they lent Abydos money in the first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.69,0:07:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The trap may have been set\nfar earlier than we realised.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.90,0:07:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Decades ago, even.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.32,0:07:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? So Kaiser played them like a damn fiddle!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.74,0:07:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they fell for this scam! {you're one to talk --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Serika.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.03,0:07:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the perpetrators\nare to blame here, not the victims.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.04,0:07:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I know that!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.75,0:08:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,People become desperate\nwhen backed into a corner.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll do anything, even if they know\nit'll only make things worse.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.22,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all this is, Serika{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.27,0:08:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The school's debt,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.23,0:08:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Abydos's current situation,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.35,0:08:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and these new discoveries we just made...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.77,0:08:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think all the pieces are starting to fall into place.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.44,0:08:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Abydos student council disbanded,\nKaiser lost the ability to buy their land.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.66,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So in order to take over this final piece of land,\nthey hired the Helmet Gang to force us out.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.54,0:08:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean the Kaiser Corporation\nwas never after the money?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.67,0:08:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Their true goal was the land itself all along?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.51,0:08:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It would make sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.72,0:08:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But that begs the question.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.80,0:08:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would anyone want to buy land\nburied under a desert?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.02,0:09:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What could they possibly stand to gain\nfrom taking over Abydos?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.90,0:09:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.03,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of the desert,\nright after we fought Gehenna...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The abandoned desert in Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.16,0:09:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(3970,4179,\c&HFDFDFD&\3c&HFDFDFD&\4c&HFDFDFD&)}The Kaiser Corporation is plotting something there.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.45,0:09:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? How does the Head Prefect\nof Gehenna know about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}, why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.54,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I mean, there was a lot going on!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.71,0:09:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like sensitive information, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.22,0:09:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, but you should have just told us!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.68,0:09:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.43,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Now we know that Kaiser\nwas the one buying out our land.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they're plotting something, we should act.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika{**-chan}'s right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.23,0:09:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The answers to all of our questions\nmust be hidden in the Abydos Desert.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.61,0:09:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.90,0:09:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Abydos Desert!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we'll have to hoof it from here.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.75,0:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't have you collapsing on us out here.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave this part to us!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.13,0:10:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, now this is a blast from the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.97,0:10:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been here before?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.06,0:10:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A few times for student council work.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.85,0:10:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit farther and we'll find\na big, grand oasis waiting for us!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What? An oasis?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.81,0:10:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.65,0:10:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a dried-up one, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.15,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's where they used to hold\nthe Abydos Oasis Festival every year.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Oasis Festival?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of that!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very well known within Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.54,0:10:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently it attracted a ton of people!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.04,0:10:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.42,0:10:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be such a big event,\nit even attracted students from other schools.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Big enough to attract them\nall the way to the desert?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.09,0:10:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thing is, from what I heard,\nthis place used to be much more hospitable.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.68,0:11:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Hoshino{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.19,0:11:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.48,0:11:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure your lead was any good?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.74,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the oasis where they\nused to hold the Oasis Festival!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a large structure ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Out here?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.84,0:11:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be what Hina was talking about.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.64,0:11:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, everyone. We don't know what's out there. {no shit ayane --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.01,0:11:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay cautious while you investigate.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.77,0:11:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.61,0:11:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's swarming with guards.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.40,0:11:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck even is this place?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser PMC.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.90,0:12:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This appears to be yet another one\nof the Kaiser Corporation's subsidiaries.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.33,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,PMC...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.70,0:12:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what it means?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.87,0:12:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,PMC stands for "Private Military Company".
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Guns-for-hire. They're mercenaries.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.92,0:12:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're nothing like the Helmet Gang.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These are professional soldiers.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.72,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Intruders?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.43,0:12:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Intruders spotted!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.81,0:12:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Get into position!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.31,0:12:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, this could get messy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prefects were already bad enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.99,0:12:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be reckless! Retreat!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who we have here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.51,0:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard we had some intruders,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.80,0:13:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wasn't expecting to find\nAbydos students at my front door.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.35,0:13:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.14,0:13:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.10,0:13:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.31,0:13:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that student council president\nGematria was interested in.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.85,0:13:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, their vice president, correct?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.27,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.57,0:13:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd expect you to know at least that much.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.53,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the director of Kaiser Corporation.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.58,0:13:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So it {\i1}was{\i0} him!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the guy behind all this?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.67,0:13:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who swindled\nthe student council out of their land?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.55,0:13:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd advise you watch your language, young lady.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.97,0:13:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're currently trespassing on the property\nof our company, Kaiser PMC.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.85,0:13:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to test my patience.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.15,0:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to the topic at hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.82,0:13:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You were asking about the land?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.23,0:14:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We did in fact purchase it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.03,0:14:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was completely legitimate, mind you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.62,0:14:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We even have the records to prove it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.49,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine you must be wondering why we\nwould purchase this barren wasteland.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be happy to explain.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.09,0:14:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking for a treasure\nsaid to be buried somewhere in Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.22,0:14:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You really expect us to believe that crap?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.93,0:14:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why do you have an army?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.77,0:14:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You were planning on taking Abydos\nby force. Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.69,0:14:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.36,0:14:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They are bodyguards to protect us from\npotential disturbances during our treasure hunt.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.19,0:14:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not here for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.74,0:14:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can deal with you whenever I want.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.29,0:14:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A phone call? Now?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.67,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.09,0:15:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got some very bad news.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.93,0:15:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.68,0:15:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.23,0:15:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They've increased our interest rate\nby three thousand percent starting next month!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do you understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.11,0:15:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're merely dogs,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm the one holding your leash.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.62,0:15:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.58,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we could pay that interest rate!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you just\ngive up and leave your school?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.87,0:15:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop out, transfer elsewhere, doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.59,0:15:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This debt is the school's responsibility.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.34,0:15:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should you, as students, carry that burden?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.68,0:15:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There's no way we could just leave!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.89,0:15:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right! We're not abandoning Abydos!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.93,0:15:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Abydos is our school. Our home!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.44,0:15:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what will it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any other options?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.15,0:16:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls. Time to go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.24,0:16:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point arguing with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just toying with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A wise choice, Miss Vice President. {SASUGA} {askcully this should be "As expected of the Vice President of Abydos"}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a smart cookie.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.05,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.38,0:16:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(6110,6220,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}I'm shocked someone so smart was willing to\nfollow that brainless idiot of a president.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.49,0:16:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then. I am eager to see those monthly repayments.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.95,0:16:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again, cherished customers,\nfor choosing Kaiser Loans.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.63,0:17:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,God! What the hell was that crap?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.17,0:17:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He said they were looking for a treasure.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.30,0:17:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Abydos collected survey reports long ago\nwhile searching for oil and other resources.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.06,0:17:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The desert is empty.\nThere's nothing of value there.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.02,0:17:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.57,0:17:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find out what they're up to.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you want to go back there?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.11,0:17:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I take time to prepare,\nI think I can infiltrate their base.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.91,0:17:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.33,0:17:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to think about\nhow to deal with the debt first.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.58,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The debt's too big. We can no longer\npay it back by playing fair.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Shiroko{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.34,0:17:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with Shiroko{**-senpai} here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If we lose the school, it's all over!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to be picky!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Think this through, Serika{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.64,0:17:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do this, it'll be no different from\nwhen we robbed the bank!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.56,0:18:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really say we saved Abydos\nif we used money we stole from elsewhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.98,0:18:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.85,0:18:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand where you're coming from,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.81,0:18:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't let you become criminals!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.28,0:18:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.66,0:18:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone.\nLet's simmer down a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see steam coming out your ears.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.49,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Shiroko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.50,0:18:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I didn't want things to get so heated.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.92,0:18:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. We know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.88,0:18:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's enough for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.96,0:18:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we all go cool off\nand meet up again tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.89,0:18:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, president's orders! Go rest!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.51,0:18:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.56,0:18:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Hoshino{*Senpai}'s right!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.92,0:19:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Entertaining useless ideas like miracles\nand happy endings, huh? {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.97,0:19:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.93,0:19:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. That's a bit cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.68,0:19:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when did you and\nmy little Shiroko{**-chan} become so close?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.52,0:19:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I could practically see you reading each other's minds.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.65,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to keep a closer eye on you, {*}Teach{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.45,0:19:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.83,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.75,0:19:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.05,0:19:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit awkward to say face to face.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.84,0:19:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if we walk and talk, {*}Teach{*Sensei}?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.35,0:20:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, {*}Teach{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.31,0:20:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,High school is supposed to be fun, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda sad if it's all covered in sand,\ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.73,0:20:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But you like this school, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.78,0:20:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that before the desert moved in,\nAbydos was known for its size and influence{/strength}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.87,0:20:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was before my time.\nI never got to see it like that myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.54,0:20:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a complete mess from day one.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.92,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't one thing the school actually got right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.01,0:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But despite all that,\nthis school is still your home, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.93,0:20:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time I enrolled, the main building\nwas already buried deep underneath the sand.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.35,0:20:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The school kept relocating as the desert expanded,\nand this annex is where it ended up.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.15,0:20:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But y'know, if I hadn't come here,\nI wouldn't have met everyone in the Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I do like this school after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.58,0:21:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a load off my chest!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.88,0:21:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If I told everyone about this,\nthey'd just worry their heads off, y'know?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.47,0:21:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know I can't go keeping secrets\nfrom my adorable little clubmates forever either.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.81,0:21:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them everything tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.73,0:21:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like they need more on their plate, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.78,0:21:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you for telling me.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.49,0:21:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll understand\nwhat you're going through.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.20,0:21:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.24,0:21:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The road ahead is long, but as long as\nwe stick together, we'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.04,0:21:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.71,0:21:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda makes you wanna wish for a miracle.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.46,0:21:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make our own miracles\nif we're all together.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.71,0:22:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.09,0:22:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough serious talk for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.09,0:22:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See you around, {*}Teach{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.10,0:22:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.93,0:22:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{=7}See you tomorrow!

